# Skills location policy

- New skills must be created under `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`.
- Do not add new references to `.agents/skills/...`.
- When updating existing docs, rules, or agent prompts, use `.cursor/skills/...` paths only.
- If an old `.agents/skills/...` reference is found, migrate it to `.cursor/skills/...` in the same change.
